'''Light Dust''' was a substance that the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] of [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]] believed responsible for rejuvenating the [[Tree of Light]].

The Tree of Light kept the [[Night Spirit/Legends|Night Spirit]] from daylight incursions into their village, and young warriors had to periodically travel to the tree to sprinkle it with Light Dust. In return, they earned a [[Silver Feather of Bravery]], and the village celebrated the [[Light Festival]].

